#: ../../D/dancing-frog.rst:9
msgid ""
"[Vancouver area] A problem that occurs on a computer that will not reappear "
"while anyone else is watching. From the classic Warner Brothers cartoon *One"
" Froggy Evening*\\, featuring a dancing and singing Michigan J. Frog that "
"just croaks when anyone else is around (now the WB network mascot)."
msgstr ""
"[Vancouver地域] "
"他の誰かが見ている間は再現しない、コンピューター上で発生する問題。誰か他の人がいるときにはただゲロゲロ鳴くだけのMichigan J. "
"Frogという踊って歌うカエルが登場する、古典的なWarner Brothersの漫画『*One Froggy "
"Evening*』に由来する(今ではWBネットワークのマスコット)。"
